Interface com.chimu.form.client.DomainObject_1

public interface DomainObject_1
DomainObject_1 is a sample domain object public interface. This is also the public interface to DomainObject_1_AbsClass implementation.

See Also:
DomaionObject_1_AbsClass

Method Index

copy()
Create a new domain object which has all its attributes copied from the current object.
delete()
Delete removes the domain object from the database.
write()
Write will either insert or update the object to the database depending on the whether it is a new object or a database replicate.
